  "publisher": "marvel",
  "about": "\"Nation X\" is a 2009–2010 crossover storyline published by Marvel Comics featuring the X-Men. Published in the aftermath of the \"Utopia\" storyline and dealing with the return of Magneto, the story appeared across several different books, including Uncanny X-Men #515–522, Nation X #1–4 and X-Men: Legacy #228–230. Its writers include James Asmus, Matt Fraction, Grace Randolph, Scott Snyder, Simon Spurrier, and Christopher Yost, and its artists include Leonard Kirk, Mike Allred, Terry Dodson, Greg Land Whilce Portacio.",
